1
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:17,159
What am I supposed to say about you?

2
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,280
You're making trouble on a tight schedule.

3
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,799
With a major safety incident like this...

4
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,560
Do you know how much the delay costs us?

5
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,920
How do I answer to the shareholders?

6
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:27,159
Can you take responsibility for this?

7
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,280
Chairman Zheng.

8
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,959
Whatever the cause of this accident,

9
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,439
it did happen on my project.

10
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,560
It was my negligence.

11
00:01:33,239 --> 00:01:34,799
I'll accept any punishment from the company.

12
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,280
But please give me three days.

13
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,879
I'll get to the bottom of this.

14
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,000
And give the company an answer.

15
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:40,799
No need.

16
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:41,879
As of now,

17
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,480
you're relieved of all your duties.

18
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,920
Bring in He Junjie from Safety.

19
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,879
He'll lead the investigation.

20
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,159
You wait for the results.

21
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,200
See for yourself.

22
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:58,400
Is the thickness of these materials up to code?

23
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,760
Why did the steel cable snap?

24
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:01,120
And why did the tower crane collapse?

25
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:03,519
Why is this substandard channel steel even here?

26
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,159
I really don't know.

27
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,879
All this was Xiao Yifan's responsibility.

28
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:10,080
Li Yao, still not going to tell the truth?

29
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,599
I really don't know!

30
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,800
Before we could haul the channel steel out,

31
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,520
the workers had already started installing it.

32
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,199
Take a good look.

33
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,319
These materials are totally substandard.

34
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,800
And you dare shift the blame

35
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,759
onto Xiao Yifan?

36
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,159
Do you know that safety incidents

37
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:26,639
carry legal liability?

38
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,080
Manager He.

39
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,159
This was all an accident.

40
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:30,840
If you don't believe me, ask the foreman.

41
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,120
You'd better not be hiding anything.

42
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,039
Or you'll bear the consequences.

43
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:38,280
Bring me all the material logs.

44
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,680
I'll verify each one back at the office.

45
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:40,680
Yes, sir.

46
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,080
Hey there.

47
00:02:59,360 --> 00:02:59,919
Sir.

48
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:02,680
You have no income while work is halted?

49
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:09,120
We get paid by the day.

50
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,759
No idea when work will resume.

51
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,759
Soon.

52
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,439
If you hauled out the bad channel steel,

53
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:17,039
the accident never would've happened.

54
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,840
And you wouldn't be losing wages now.

55
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,280
Manager Xiao didn't let us haul it away.

56
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:25,400
He's the one in charge of this project.

57
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,319
He knew the angle steel was substandard,

58
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:29,039
but still made us install it overnight.

59
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:31,560
It was windy and about to rain that day.

60
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:33,000
He made us break safety protocol.

61
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,360
That's what caused the accident.

62
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:35,479
I bet,

63
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:37,680
Xiao Yifan definitely took bribes on this.

64
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,199
How do you know he took bribes?

65
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:45,680
We all know Xiao Yifan has shares in this.

66
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,919
By day, he pretended to have us remove it.

67
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:49,719
By night, he made us install it.

68
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,639
And look,

69
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:52,400
it collapsed.

70
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,360
You're back.

71
00:04:11,599 --> 00:04:12,400
Yeah, I'm back.

72
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,600
What's wrong?

73
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,920
You look like a deflated balloon.

74
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,879
Where's the kid?

75
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:25,399
He's already asleep.

76
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:30,240
How's the site investigation going?

77
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:36,920
I feel Xiao Yifan's hiding things from me.

78
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,079
Hiding things?

79
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:40,800
Like what?

80
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,399
He might have taken bribes.

81
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,480
What?

82
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,000
Have you actually looked into it properly?

83
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,920
How much more can I look into it?

84
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,879
The foreman told me everything in detail.

85
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,720
Would a worker frame a project manager?

86
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:57,959
Why are you snapping at me?

87
00:04:58,319 --> 00:05:00,959
I just suggest you look into it properly.

88
00:05:00,959 --> 00:05:02,959
Don't doubt your own bro so easily.

89
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,879
Your industry comes with huge temptations.

90
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:13,079
If Xiao Yifan really did take bribes,

91
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:15,079
you should confront him face to face.

92
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:16,759
And see if he's really gone corrupt.

93
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,079
Grandma.

94
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:50,000
When I grow up, I'll build lots of tall,

95
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,600
beautiful houses for you to live in.

96
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:56,360
Wonderful, Grandma will be waiting.

97
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,560
Thank you.

98
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,199
(Colleagues applaud)

99
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:32,519
You're suspended. Wait for the results.

100
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:35,959
Come, read this to Daddy.

101
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:38,560
The sky went completely dark.

102
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,000
Sweetie, go play upstairs for a bit.

103
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,040
I need to talk with your uncle.

104
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:45,319
Okay, Daddy.

105
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,680
Bye, Uncle He.

106
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,759
Good girl.

107
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,959
Ask whatever you want.

108
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:01,199
Did you take money from Fang Bing or not?

109
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:05,439
Even you don't believe me?

110
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,000
I asked if you have shares with Fang Bing.

111
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,279
I clearly told him

112
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,160
to haul those substandard materials away.

113
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,040
He ordered the workers himself that night

114
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,079
to break protocol, causing the accident.

115
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:18,120
Tower cranes can't work in wind or rain!

116
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:19,759
I'm asking if you took bribes.

117
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:21,560
And shares with Fang Bing and suppliers?

118
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,839
Who told you that?

119
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,000
Who told you?

120
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,079
This is a frame-up.

121
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:26,839
A frame-up!

122
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,920
Would a worker dare frame a boss like you?

123
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,959
Who said it?

124
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,319
Bring him here to confront me.

125
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:34,000
We're bros, yet even you don't trust me?

126
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,240
I want to believe you too.

127
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,439
But all evidence points to you.

128
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,319
How do you explain that to me?

129
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:38,959
How will you explain it?

130
00:07:39,079 --> 00:07:39,560
Go on, explain!

131
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,000
Are you two done arguing?

132
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,480
If you've argued enough, come up for dinner.

133
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,560
I've got things to do. I'll skip dinner.

134
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,240
Honey.

135
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:04,240
I believe Xiao Yifan would never take bribes.

136
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,160
You two have been bros since college.

137
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:09,759
You know exactly what kind of man he is.

138
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,519
But that worker had no grudge against him.

139
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,439
Why would he falsely accuse him?

140
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:19,199
I just feel like

141
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:21,240
something isn't quite right.

142
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:24,160
What exactly feels off?

143
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:27,319
A woman's intuition.

144
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,120
I'm sure there's a problem here.

145
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,759
You should look into it more carefully.

146
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,919
Ah!

147
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,360
Manager He.

148
00:10:23,559 --> 00:10:24,480
What do you want?

149
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,440
You waited for me at the site on purpose

150
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,679
to mislead me with those words,

151
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:28,440
didn't you?

152
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:30,720
What... what are you saying?

153
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,639
I don't understand.

154
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:33,960
You're quite good at playing dumb.

155
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,600
I've been watching you for a while now.

156
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:36,960
The site's been shut down,

157
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,480
yet you're spending lavishly every day.

158
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,240
Talk!

159
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:40,440
Where did that money come from?

160
00:10:40,559 --> 00:10:41,840
Who told you to frame Xiao Yifan?

161
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:43,720
Manager He,

162
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:44,279
you...

163
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:45,320
You must be mistaken.

164
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,759
The money I've been spending

165
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,480
is what I saved up before.

166
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:50,200
And I didn't mislead you.

167
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:52,240
You approached me first that day,

168
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,480
so I told you what I knew.

169
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:54,440
Ah!

170
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:57,919
Still lying!

171
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,919
Don't you know framing someone means jail?

172
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:00,639
Move!

173
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,759
Come with me to the police station.

174
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,679
Mr. He!

175
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:03,639
Ah!

176
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:05,720
I'll talk!

177
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,639
I'll talk!

178
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:08,440
Talk!
